00:28:07.060 --> 00:28:09.540
because we do what
we call liberty.

00:28:09.540 --> 00:28:11.400
And there are very playful.

00:28:11.400 --> 00:28:12.670
That's why we like them.

00:28:12.670 --> 00:28:16.370
And also, they like
to stay in herds

00:28:16.370 --> 00:28:17.870
more than the other horses.

00:28:17.870 --> 00:28:23.300
They are very inclined
to be part of a group.

00:28:23.300 --> 00:28:25.300
So when we do
liberty, at one point,

00:28:25.300 --> 00:28:27.930
there's about 12 horses coming.

00:28:27.930 --> 00:28:32.570
it depends on the
show, from 8 to 12.

00:28:32.570 --> 00:28:37.140
But they all behave together,
and they all act together,

00:28:37.140 --> 00:28:38.360
and they're totally free.

00:28:38.360 --> 00:28:39.670
And there's one girl.

00:28:39.670 --> 00:28:40.820
Her name is Elise Verdoncq.

00:28:40.820 --> 00:28:44.800
She's the main trainer
for those horses.

00:28:44.800 --> 00:28:48.166
And also, I think
they're very elegant.

00:28:48.166 --> 00:28:49.540
And the Arabian,
for the ones who

00:28:49.540 --> 00:28:53.000
don't know, when they
start to be happy,

00:28:53.000 --> 00:28:55.050
it's a little bit like
the dogs with the tails,

